I'm actually a musician too, and I've covered a few of his songs on my channel. A few weeks ago I covered "Adore You," and it's definitely some of my best work. I'd love to cover "Falling" at some point too :) I'm just a guy with a dream, so if you want to check it out, that would mean so much to me. If not, I get that too :) hope you guys are all enjoying the new album! 🤘🏻🖤
